# No prefers-reduced-motion

This codebase intentionally does not implement `prefers-reduced-motion` handling.

Do not add:
- `@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)` CSS blocks
- `window.matchMedia('(prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)')` checks
- `prefersReducedMotion()` helpers or similar guards

Animations, transitions, parallax, and carousels should always run as designed.
